<div class="text-center">
  <!-- Terminal-style ASCII header -->
  <pre class="text-orange-500 text-xs sm:text-sm mb-4 leading-tight">
 ███████╗████████╗███████╗██╗     ██╗      █████╗ ██████╗ ██████╗
 ██╔════╝╚══██╔══╝██╔════╝██║     ██║     ██╔══██╗██╔══██╗██╔══██╗
 ███████╗   ██║   █████╗  ██║     ██║     ███████║██████╔╝██████╔╝
 ╚════██║   ██║   ██╔══╝  ██║     ██║     ██╔══██║██╔══██╗██╔══██╗
 ███████║   ██║   ███████╗███████╗███████╗██║  ██║██║  ██║██████╔╝
 ╚══════╝   ╚═╝   ╚══════╝╚══════╝╚══════╝╚═╝  ╚═╝╚═╝  ╚═╝╚═════╝
  </pre>
  <p class="text-lime-400 mb-8 text-sm">[ Stellar Arbitrage Trading System v1.0.0 ]</p>

  <div class="bg-blue-900 border-2 border-orange-500 p-6 text-left">
    <!-- Terminal header bar -->
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-blue-700">
      <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500"></span>
      <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></span>
      <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500"></span>
      <span class="ml-2 text-gray-400 text-xs">stellarb-auth@terminal</span>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-2 text-sm mb-6">
      <p><span class="text-lime-400">$</span> system.init()</p>
      <p class="text-gray-400">Initializing authentication module...</p>
      <p><span class="text-lime-400">$</span> auth.request_access()</p>
      <p class="text-gray-400">Enter pilot credentials to continue:</p>
    </div>

    <%= form_with model: @user, url: sessions_path, local: true, class: "space-y-4" do |f| %>
      <div>
        <label class="block text-sm mb-1">
          <span class="text-lime-400">&gt;</span> EMAIL_ADDRESS:
        </label>
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <span class="text-orange-500 mr-2">│</span>
          <%= f.email_field :email,
              class: "flex-1 px-3 py-3 sm:py-2 bg-blue-950 border border-blue-700 rounded font-mono text-base text-lime-400 focus:border-orange-500 focus:outline-none placeholder-gray-600 min-h-[44px]",
              placeholder: "pilot@stellarb.net",
              required: true,
              autofocus: true,
              autocomplete: "email" %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-2">
        <%= f.submit "[ TRANSMIT ACCESS REQUEST ]",
            class: "w-full bg-orange-500 text-blue-950 font-bold py-3 sm:py-2 px-4 border-2 border-orange-400 hover:bg-orange-400 hover:border-orange-300 transition-colors cursor-pointer tracking-wider min-h-[44px] text-base" %>
      </div>
    <% end %>

    <div class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-blue-700 text-xs space-y-1">
      <p class="text-gray-400"><span class="text-lime-400">INFO:</span> A one-time access code will be transmitted to your comm unit.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-500"><span class="text-orange-500">DEV:</span> Auto-login enabled for development mode.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8 text-xs text-gray-500 space-y-1">
    <p class="text-gray-600">─────────────────────────────────────────</p>
    <p>You are traveling through space.</p>
    <p>It's like a maze of twisty passages that look all alike,</p>
    <p>but that's another game. This game has lasers.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-600">─────────────────────────────────────────</p>
  </div>
</div>
